name: Memcached Web Admin
tagline: Keep tabs on your memcached instance with a web interface.
body:
# Memcached Web Admin

With the closing of Google Code and the [phpMemcachedAdmin](https://code.google.com/p/phpmemcacheadmin/) project no longer maintained regularly, this is a fork intended to keep the project alive and updated.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
